.RH MOD.RECIPES-SOURCE RLZ-RUM-BALLS C "29 Dec 86" 1987
.RZ "RUM BALLS" "Zeek Rum Balls"
Robin Zeek's famous rum balls. A great holiday treat.
.IH "Makes 2\(12 dozen"
.IG "2\(12 cups" "crushed vanilla wafers" "400 g"
.IG "1 cup" "crushed walnuts" "120 g"
.IG "2 Tbsp" "cocoa" "30 ml"
.IG "3 Tbsp" "dark corn syrup" "5 cl"
.IG "\(14 cup" "rum" "6 cl"
.IG "1 cup" "powdered sugar" "130 g"
.PH
.SK 1
Mix all of the above ingredients in a large bowl.
.SK 2
Roll the mixture into small balls.
.SK 3
Roll the balls in powdered sugar.
.NX
You can substitute your favorite spirits for the rum.
.SH RATING
.I Difficulty:
easy to moderate.  How good were you in kindergarten clay-1?
.I Time:
15 minutes preparation, 15 minutes rolling and powdering.
.I Precision:
measure the ingredients.
.WR
Robin Zeek
AT&T Network Systems, Columbus, Ohio, USA
